<body>
<p>Reports unresolved Spring beans referenced in <a href="https://spring.io/projects/spring-security">Spring Security</a> annotations.</p>

<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <pre><code>@WithUserDetails(value = "admin", userDetailsServiceBeanName = "unknownUserDetailsService")
      // "Cannot resolve 'unknownUserDetailsService' bean" will be reported if 'unknownUserDetailsService' is not defined in the Spring model
    </code></pre>
  </li>
  <li>
    <pre><code>@WithUserDetails(value = "admin", userDetailsServiceBeanName = "jpaUserDetailsService")
      //"Bean must be of 'org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetailsService' type"
      // will be reported if "jpaUserDetailsService"  bean is not of 'UserDetailsService' type
    </code></pre>
  </li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>